// Tartans
//
// Various tartans from the Scottish Register of Tartans:
// https://www.tartanregister.gov.uk
//
// Current sequence: Buchanan (1850), Hunting Stewart, Macbeth, Macleod,
// Fraser (1745), Thomson Dress Blue, Black Watch Plaid of Pipers, St.
// Piran's Cornish Flag and the FBI.
//
// <mouse>: pan image or modify colours (depending on 'm' key)
// <left>/<right>: select tartan
// <up>/<down>: scale
// <page up>/<page down>: multiply threadcount
// m: select mouse mode - pan or colouring
// h: only modify colours on LHS.
// 
// Display currently just solid blocks of colour (threads 1 pixel wide
// by default, <up>/<down> scales, and <page up>/<page down>
// multiplies threadcount).
//
// RGB for colours taken from the Register. Use mouse to modify
// colours (press 'm' key to enable) - x axis controls brightness, y
// axis mixes in a dull tan for an attempt at a "weathered" look.
//
